ERRATA.

VOL. LXXIX.

Page 171. after $+n \cdot \frac{n-1}{2} \cdot \frac{n-2}{3} \log_r - 3p + \&c.$ is omitted but $\log_r - n \times \log_r - p + n \cdot \frac{n-1}{2} \log_r - 2p - n \cdot \frac{n-1}{2} \cdot \frac{n-2}{3} \times \log_r - 3p + \&c.$ =, which probably happened, in my absence from the press, on account of the similarity of the preceding quantity.
